        "body": "<p>Aliangé's Jellyfish Peptide X Antioxidant Serum uses advanced peptide technology designed to support skin structure and protect against environmental stress.</p><p><strong>Acetyl Hexapeptide-51 Amide</strong> — This peptide is studied for its ability to support DNA protection within skin cells. It helps strengthen the skin's natural defence mechanisms against environmental damage.</p><p><strong>Palmitoyl Tripeptide-38</strong> — A peptide associated with supporting the skin's extracellular matrix, which contributes to the structural network that maintains skin firmness and elasticity.</p><p>Together these peptides help support collagen production, skin elasticity, structural resilience, and reduction in visible fine lines.</p>",
